Package: SkeletalVis
Type: Package
Title: Exploration and visualisation of skeletal transcriptomics data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jamie Soul
Maintainer: Jamie Soul <jamie.soul@liverpool.ac.uk>
Description: Allows search and visualisation of a collection of uniformly processed skeletal transcriptomic datasets.
    Users can find datasets where genes of intererest are differentially expressed and find datasets with a similar gene expression pattern to their own data.
